---
title: Melty Mozzarella Burgers with Caramelized Onion and Balsamic Greens on Ciabatta
description: Burgers are about as all-American as you can get. But that doesn’t mean they don’t have dreams of voyaging to faraway places. These patties on ciabatta are what happens when cheeseburgers take a trip to Italy. Between the sweetness of the caramelized onion on top, the way the mozzarella melts into loose strands, and the tangy kick brought by balsamic vinegar dressing, you could say these burgers are loaded with dolce vita attitude.
